{"tid":2149200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道指有美資銀行已開始暫停受美國制裁人士關連賬戶","createTime":"2020-08-10T09:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T09:39:05.000Z","uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3358692a93df885a1f45ff63d17586220a78f3c5","tid":2149200,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"美國財政部上週公布制裁本港及內地11名官員，《彭博》引述消息人士指，本港一間美資銀行已開始暫停與被制裁人士相關的賬戶，另有兩間中資銀行亦正檢視是否需要更新其合規要求。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，滙控(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=9871433c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>) 及花旗拒就報道作出評論，中國銀行(<a href=\"http://03988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03988.HK&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=5fd11a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03988.HK</a>)  及工商銀行(<a href=\"http://01398.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01398.HK&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=6b68d2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01398.HK</a>)  則尚未回應查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1033966/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1033966%2F2&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=088ff0e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1033966/2</a>"},{"pid":"7515cf8633a50246b1f68111d3a205cc32a1df83","tid":2149200,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95152fbbc80a0d1ee61fd2ea5a48e160a5a105ce","tid":2149200,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:38:04.000Z","ms